mi-alpena-golf-club
Description: Alpena Golf Club allows you to experience two different styles of golf courses in a single round. The front nine’s personality reflects an authentic 1930’s style design with larger landing areas, mature trees, and smaller greens. Venture to Alpena’s back nine to play a more contemporary course designed by Warner Bowen. Here you will find longer holes, larger contoured greens and wooded rolling terrain with several ponds.
